de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.datasource.bundle

Class BundleWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.datasource.bundle.BundleWriter

  • public class BundleWriter
extends Object
    Write an object bundle stream to a file channel. Bundle streams that add new columns are not supported.
